:uqshrl^ItCond thv_RdaLo, thv_RdaHi, qShift is $(TMODE_E) & ItCond & thv_c2427=0xa & thv_c2023=0x5 & thv_RdaLo & thv_c1616=1 & thv_RdaHi & thv_c0808=1 & thv_c1515=0 & qShift & thv_c0405=1 & thv_c0003=0xf {
